Class FlowPointEdge

    • edu.utsa.fileflow.cfg.FlowPointEdge

  • public class FlowPointEdge
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an edge in a ControlFlowGraph. This edge should serve as a directed edge to connect two FlowPoint objects.
